title: Your Future Begins!
posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 915 Sq.', 'Ft.', "They say home isn't a place, but a feeling.", "Located in the lovely little suburb of Lakewood, Colorado, Lakeview Heights Apartments' pet-friendly one and two bedroom apartments come with all the modern conveniences to help you create a space that's just right for you.", 'Plus, community perks like a resort-style pool make coming home a celebration of the everyday.', "All this and more surrounded by natural beauty that's truly breathtaking to behold.", 'Features:', 'Modern, Open Living Area, Air Conditioning & Ceiling Fans, Spacious Floor Plans Designed For You, Pet-Friendly Living - Dogs & Cats Welcome!, Vinyl, Wood-Style Flooring, 1 & 2 Bedroom Floor Plans, Polished & Resurfaced Countertops, New Appliances', 'Community Amenities:', 'Off Street Parking, Community Picnic Area With Pergola, Open Natural Spaces & Trail System, Resort-Inspired Swimming Pool, BBQ & Picnic Area, Close to the Light Rail, Onsite Laundry Facility, Ideal Location Near Lakeview Heights, Landscaped Grounds', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet-Friendly Living - Dogs & Cats Welcome!', 'Breed Restrictions Apply.', 'Income Requirements:', 'Combined gross monthly income of 2.5x the rent amount.', 'Use this link for more information:', '<URL>', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', '4j3wdyy98W']
